  <md:title>The Spanish-American War and Overseas Empire</md:title>
  <md:abstract>By the end of this section, you will be able to:
<list>
<item>Explain the origins and events of the Spanish-American War</item>
<item>Analyze the different American opinions on empire at the conclusion of the Spanish-American War</item>
<item>Describe how the Spanish-American War intersected with other American expansions to solidify the nation’s new position as an empire</item>
</list></md:abstract>
  <md:uuid>e12cea15-aa6f-43d5-9f0f-6a1df689f8e2</md:uuid>
